384
00:43:42,197 --> 00:43:44,656
Remember Pythagoras.

385
00:43:44,781 --> 00:43:50,323
Mathematician, cult leader.
Athens, circa 500 BC.

386
00:43:50,406 --> 00:43:55,239
Major belief: The universe
is made of numbers.

387
00:43:55,364 --> 00:43:58,031
Major contribution:

388
00:43:58,114 --> 00:44:01,156
The golden ratio.

389
00:44:02,905 --> 00:44:06,989
Best represented geometrically
as the golden rectangle.

390
00:44:07,114 --> 00:44:09,615
Visually, there exists
a graceful equilibrium

391
00:44:09,740 --> 00:44:11,364
between its length and width.

392
00:44:12,489 --> 00:44:17,364
When it's squared, it leaves a
smaller golden rectangle behind,

393
00:44:17,489 --> 00:44:19,947
with the same unique ratio.

394
00:44:20,072 --> 00:44:24,531
The squaring can continue,
smaller and smaller,

395
00:44:24,656 --> 00:44:25,864
to infinity.

396
00:44:59,156 --> 00:45:01,947
11:18. More evidence.

397
00:45:02,072 --> 00:45:06,406
Remember da Vinci. Artist,
inventor, sculptor, naturalist.

398
00:45:06,531 --> 00:45:09,114
ltaly, C15th.

399
00:45:09,239 --> 00:45:11,947
Rediscovered the perfection
of the golden rectangle

400
00:45:12,114 --> 00:45:16,114
and pencilled it
into his masterpieces.

401
00:45:16,239 --> 00:45:20,239
Connecting a curve through the
concentric golden rectangles,

402
00:45:20,364 --> 00:45:24,281
You generate the mythical
golden spiral.

403
00:45:24,406 --> 00:45:27,615
Pythagoras loved this shape,
for he found it in nature -

404
00:45:27,739 --> 00:45:31,323
a nautilus shell, rams' horns,
whirlpools, tornadoes,

405
00:45:31,448 --> 00:45:35,739
our fingerprints, our DNA
and even our Milky Way.

406
00:45:36,573 --> 00:45:38,615
9:22. Personal note.

407
00:45:38,739 --> 00:45:41,114
When I was a little kid,

408
00:45:41,239 --> 00:45:44,489
my mother told me
not to stare into the sun.

409
00:45:44,615 --> 00:45:46,739
So once, I did.

410
00:45:46,864 --> 00:45:49,114
At first, the brightness
was overwhelming,

411
00:45:49,239 --> 00:45:52,114
but I kept looking,
forcing myself not to blink.

412
00:45:52,239 --> 00:45:54,864
And then the brightness
began to dissolve.

413
00:45:54,947 --> 00:45:59,864
My pupils shrank to pinholes
and everything came into focus.

414
00:45:59,989 --> 00:46:02,780
And for a moment I understood.

415
00:46:02,906 --> 00:46:06,947
My new hypothesis:
if we're built from spirals,

416
00:46:07,072 --> 00:46:09,364
while living in a giant spiral,

417
00:46:09,490 --> 00:46:13,989
then everything we do
is infused with the spiral.

